    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8100315/" class="title-link">实用主义最大价值或许在于和稀泥</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8100315"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/102112872/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u102112872-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/102112872/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">OUC朝闻道</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
